  <div class="slide-divider">↓</div>

  <!-- ============================================================
       SLIDE 3 — NPS Alegra
       ============================================================ -->
  <div class="slide">
    <div class="slide-header">
      <span class="title">NPS Alegra Accounting</span>
      <span class="period">{{ config.quarter_label }}</span>
    </div>
    <div class="slide-body" style="padding: 14px 28px 10px; flex-direction: row; gap: 20px; overflow: hidden;">
      <!-- Imagen NPS -->
      <div style="flex: 1 1 0; min-width: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 8px; overflow: hidden;">
        <img src="data:image/png;base64," style="max-width: 100%; max-height: 48%; object-fit: contain; border-radius: 6px;" />
        <img src="data:image/png;base64," style="max-width: 100%; max-height: 48%; object-fit: contain; border-radius: 6px;" />
      </div>
      <!-- Panel de insights -->
      <div style="flex: 0 0 260px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0;">
        <div style="font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.4px; color: #1e3a8a; border-bottom: 1.5px solid #e2e8f0; padding-bottom: 6px; margin-bottom: 8px;">Key Insights</div>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 7px;">
          <div style="font-size: 9px; line-height: 1.45; color: #374151;"><span style="font-weight: 700; color: #0f172b;">Support Access: </span>Users report difficulty reaching support, even when paying for phone attention plans that were never delivered.</div>
          <div style="font-size: 9px; line-height: 1.45; color: #374151;"><span style="font-weight: 700; color: #0f172b;">System Stability: </span>The platform crashes frequently when issuing and printing invoices, affecting business operational continuity.</div>
          <div style="font-size: 9px; line-height: 1.45; color: #374151;"><span style="font-weight: 700; color: #0f172b;">Accounting Complexity: </span>The accounting module is perceived as complex and unintuitive, with unreliable tax reports and invoicing discrepancies.</div>
          <div style="font-size: 9px; line-height: 1.45; color: #374151;"><span style="font-weight: 700; color: #0f172b;">Pricing &amp; Plans: </span>The Emprendedor plan is seen as too restrictive, and overall pricing is considered high relative to current platform performance.</div>
          <div style="font-size: 9px; line-height: 1.45; color: #374151;"><span style="font-weight: 700; color: #0f172b;">Automation Gaps: </span>Existing automations have significant failures and fall short of user expectations.</div>
          <div style="font-size: 9px; line-height: 1.45; color: #374151;"><span style="font-weight: 700; color: #0f172b;">Costa Rica: </span>Did not receive any NPS responses in March 2026.</div>
          <div style="font-size: 9px; line-height: 1.45; color: #374151;">It&#39;s important to note that the NPS methodologies for February and March differed. In February, responses were collected exclusively through in-app pop-up messages. In March, the approach was split: 50% of responses came from pop-up messages and the remaining 50% from inbox notifications within the product.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="slide-footer">
      <span class="footer-brand">Alegra · Confidential</span>
      <span class="footer-page">3</span>
    </div>
